How Browser Understands HTML
When you open: https://algonex.com
Browser
↓
Downloads HTML
↓
Creates DOM (Document Object Model)
    ↓
Downloads CSS
    ↓
Downloads JS
↓
Renders Page # So HTML is the first file every browser reads

