Why DOCTYPE?                   | Enables standards mode (HTML5)                                        
Why Semantic HTML?             | SEO + Accessibility + Maintainability                                 
Difference div vs span?        | Block vs Inline                                                       
Difference id vs class?        | Unique vs Reusable                                                    
Why alt attribute?             | Accessibility + fallback if image fails                               
Why viewport?                  | Mobile responsiveness                                                 
Difference section vs article? | 'section' groups related content; 'article' is self-contained content 
Why one h1?                    | Clear document hierarchy for users and search engines                 


