## Before moving to CSS, you should be able to answer these questions confidently
-> Why do we use <!DOCTYPE html>?
-> What is the purpose of the <head> element?
-> Why is the viewport meta tag important?
-> What's the difference between block and inline elements?
-> When should you use <section> instead of <div>?
-> Why should every image have an alt attribute?
-> Why should there usually be only one <h1> on a page?
